_sText:
**This map is designed for gg and dm modes.**


This map includes:

- Swinging signs on the walls made with phys_ballsockets
- Cubemaps
- 4 luxel- ground for awesome shadows
- Support for 52 players for crazy gameplay
- AN ORANGE!

Making of this map took me about 4 days.
About one to six hours per day.

Note, that this is my first _published_ map.
The file is 8mb, but it is really worth it!


Oh, and remember to send some feedback for me so I can make it better!
